%^BOLD%^-=%^BLUE%^Protection Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

This domain grants its users the ability to protect 
themselves and their surroundings in various ways.  
Not only will it offer some protection in battle, but 
it will also aid in preventing certain magical spells
and effects.

The protection domain contains the following spells:
Divine Shield (2nd), Invisibility Purge (5th), Teleportation Ward (8th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Jarmila, Kreysneothosies

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     